replies.body:
If solo que, your team has 1 gold player, a bot, a bronze or a silver, and two iron. Their team has a bot, a bronze or two, maybe a silver, and two iron. Probably. More often than not.

Your team will have a better chance. Especially if you, the gold, can lead. Remember that positive behavior positively affects the team. With those three advantages (skill advantage, leadership, and positivity), you're gonna get out of iron real fast.

